《'''失落的秘符'''》（{{lang-en|''The Lost Symbol''}}），-{zh-hans:[[臺灣|台]]译《'''失落的符号'''》;zh-hant:中國譯《'''失落的秘符'''》}-，原名《所罗门之钥》，是[[美国|美国]]著名畅销书作家[[丹·布朗|丹·布朗]]于2009年9月15日出版的暢銷[[小說|小說]]。<ref name="bostonheraldannounce">{{cite web|url=http://bostonherald.com/entertainment/books/view/2009_04_20_Dan_Brown_announces_new_book___The_Lost_Symbol_/srvc=home&position=recent|title=Dan Brown announces new book, 'The Lost Symbol'|accessdate=2009-04-20|date=2009-04-20|first=Gina|last=Carbone|publisher=[[Boston_Herald|Boston Herald]]|archive-date=2012-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120222014659/http://bostonherald.com/entertainment/books/view/2009_04_20_Dan_Brown_announces_new_book___The_Lost_Symbol_/srvc%3Dhome%26position%3Drecent|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ETSolomon>{{Cite web |url=http://www.etonline.com/news/2009/02/70741/ |title="ET Breaks News: Dan Brown Has Finished New Book" ETonline, February 12, 2009 |accessdate=2009-12-26 |archive-date=2009-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090504093824/http://www.etonline.com/news/2009/02/70741/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=ETSolomon/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.seacoastonline.com/articles/20090212-ENTERTAIN-90212038|author=|title=Report: Dan Brown has finished his book|publisher=Seacoastonlone.com|accessdate=2009-02-12|archive-date=2009-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090216063806/http://seacoastonline.com/articles/20090212-ENTERTAIN-90212038|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Dan Brown is ready with new book (Swedish: Dan Brown klar med ny bok) | publisher = E24 Lifestyle | date = 2009-02-13 | url = http://www.e24.se/lifestyle/kultur/artikel_1086361.e24 | accessdate = 2009-02-13 }}</ref>本书的主人公与2000年出版的《[[天使与魔鬼|天使与魔鬼]]》、2003年出版的《[[達文西密碼|達文西密碼]]》一样<ref name="bostonheraldannounce" />，仍是[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]][[符号学|符号学]][[教授|教授]][[罗伯特·兰登|罗伯特·兰登]]，场景设定在[[美國|美國]][[首都|首都]][[华盛顿特区|华盛顿特区]]，以[[共济会|共济会]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://community.middlebury.edu/~beyer/sk/index.htm|author=|title=Keys to Dan Brown's Solomon Key|accessdate=2008-12-20|archive-date=2012-07-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68uOuw8X2?url=http://community.middlebury.edu/~beyer/sk/index.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和[[希伯来|希伯来]]古书《所罗门之钥》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.keyofsolomon.net/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-12-15 |archive-date=2017-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171105234416/http://www.keyofsolomon.net/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>中的神秘符号为主题。本书已完成多年，曾被猜测于2006年付梓，但出版日期几经推迟<ref name=Bookseller1>{{cite web|url=http://www.thebookseller.com/news/83123-random-house-announces-dan-brown-date.html|title=Random House announces Dan Brown date|last=Neill|first=Graeme|date=2009-04-20|publisher=[[The_Bookseller|The Bookseller]]|accessdate=2009-04-20|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090423103238/http://www.thebookseller.com/news/83123-random-house-announces-dan-brown-date.html|archivedate=2009-04-23}}</ref>，最终定于2009年9月15日。预计首批印刷数量将多达五百万到六百五十万本，将创下Random House首印数量之最。本书的电子版面市的日期官方尚未公布<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/15/books/15ebooks.html?_r=1&hpw|title=A New World: Scheduling E-Books|date=2009-07-15|publisher=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|accessdate=2009-07-15|archive-date=2018-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929161053/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/15/books/15ebooks.html?_r=1&hpw|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idUSTRE5670T120090708|title=Dan Brown moves to Washington for new thriller|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2009-07-08|accessdate=2009-07-15|archive-date=2009-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090712004216/http://www.reuters.com/article/entertainmentNews/idUSTRE5670T120090708|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但已开始接受预定。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/B002KQ6BT6/16041987-20|title=The Lost Symbol eBook（Kindle Version）
